import App from "./App.js"
import ReactDOM from "react-dom"
import {Router,Routes,Route } from "react-router-dom"
ReactDOM.render(
    <React.StrictMode>
      <BrowserRouter>
        <Routes>
          <Route path="/" element={ <App/> }>
          </Route>
        </Routes>
      </BrowserRouter>
    </React.StrictMode>,
    document.getElementById('root')
  );
